// IntroString :
"P2563050938" "Vanessa DeVore's Carnival of Shadows continually recruits the young and rich of Paragon's high society. These young women will not be the last to fall for her promises.<br><br>They may even believe they are joining of their own free will, but you're confident that they can still be saved. The debauch is probably in full swing by now, so expect heavy Carnival resistance. After all, you are trying to take away their playthings."
