// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL8-9_Task_01 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P115647037" "The young and rich who flock to the Carnival of Shadows need to learn that there are serious consequences to their actions. These young victims won't be the last by far, and unless you take a stand the number will only continue to grow.<br><br>One thing that might stand a chance of getting through their thick skulls is the harsh reality that heroes arrest Carnival members - regardless of the length of their membership. By taking these debutantes down on the very day of their induction, their peers might think twice about the Carnival as a life choice."
// AcceptString :
"P3554748969" "See that the debutantes' careers as Carnies are the shortest on record."
// SendOffString :
"P1242975575" "The party will be in full swing soon. That will be the time to strike and put an early end to the festivities."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P831679815" "Defeat the Debutantes!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3832482828" "The best way to resolve this problem is to teach these young wannabe Carnies what happens to those that join a criminal organization.  You set off to teach these women a grim lesson."
// TaskTitle :
"P1306728888" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Elegant Party Favor</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P227493211" "As you enter you hear an ear-splitting cheer. The guests of honor have just put on their masks."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2102029575" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Elegant Party Favor</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You arrested the debutantes at their own induction ceremony. Young socialites everywhere now fear the same treatment.  Now maybe they'll think twice and truly consider their options before joining up with these villains."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P3412260197" "This debutante has just put on her mask for the first time tonight."
