"P687000544" "The death mask collection is tempting bait for the Carnival, but they mustn't be allowed to get their hands on it. The heist is probably already in progress at the storage location for the masks. If you know the Carnies, they're not going to be stopped by whatever security has been arranged.<br><br>You have to get there and put a stop to the heist by taking our their ringleader and securing the death masks."
