"P2768967256" "These charges will readily take out even a reinforced laboratory. Just make sure to keep a safe distance."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P940819680" "The Crey scientists captured by the Devouring Earth are already as good as dead. Yet if you know Crey, they've already restaffed and are back to whatever diabolical manufacturing they were up to. If that lab isn't shut down, the environmental damage could continue unabated.<br><br>They have enough lawyers on hand to tangle whatever legal route is being taken to stop the lab for decades. There's only one way to shut it down, and that's with your own two hands... and some explosive charges."
// AcceptString :
"P2380280394" "Destroy the polluting Crey laboratory before they can recover."
// SendOffString :
"P3786290702" "Security will be on high alert and increased patrols due to the recent attack. You'd better stay alert."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3115331979" "Destroy the Polluting Lab!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1781159055" "You're tired of having your hands bound by red tape and bureaucracy!  It's time for Crey to pay for their crimes.  You set off with explosives in tow to teach Crey a lesson."
// TaskTitle :
"P2112586591" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Scrawled Bark</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

