// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3973823719" "You're well aware that the Malta Organization is planning some sort of trap for you. If you try to save the political organizer, they'll be waiting in force. Unfortunately, you can't risk the life of the target by avoiding the ambush.<br><br>Instead, you're just going to have to walk in there and deal with whatever they have in store. The best you can do is be on your guard and do what's right."
// AcceptString :
"P3823593347" "Protect the political organizer from Malta."
// SendOffString :
"P1318242393" "Malta is waiting for you. You have a bad feeling about this."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P304369969" "Protect Malta's target!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3612115817" "You need to get that thing taken care off we talked about earlier."
// TaskTitle :
"P493266226" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Blatantly Fake Malta Plans</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2964880517" "Seems as though Malta has already done a number on this place. Hopefully their bait is still alive."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2055992596" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Blatantly Fake Malta Plans</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You braved an obvious Malta trap to save an innocent bystander.  You were prepared for this sort of scenario and came out more or less unscathed."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P240730268" "<shout>Any sign of {HeroName}?"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1013508297" "{HeroName}! What a surprise!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1929594178" "<shout>They always come, the fools."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3459752619" "Commander Pike"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P3152408658" "The Tac Ops Commanders are the only members of their cell to have any contact with the upper echelons of the Malta group. Secrecy and maintaining their cover identity is the primary directive for these agents."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1242990015" "<shout>This is Pike. All reserve units deploy now!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3713242302" "<shout>Looks like we caught you good, hero."
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P3194660468" "I'll enjoy this too."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2113140978" "Did you enjoy reading our secrets?<em>I enjoyed writing those lies myself."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P546933057" "<shout>Reinforcements!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P414894925" "You're tougher... than you are smart."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P2831358790" "How... did you..."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P2985995389" "Mission accomplished!"

