// Task - AM_Vig_SL8-9_Task_04 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - SelfDestruct 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3379014107" "Self-Destruct Codes"
// DetailString :
"P1710346516" "These codes will cause the Malta cell's base to shut down and self-destruct."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1140821687" "The Malta Organization cell which spawned this trap is betting that you have to take the bait if they pretend an innocent is in jeopardy. You're smarter than that.<br><br>There's no gain to them taking out their hostage if you don't fall for the trap. All you have to do is trail the group after they abandon their plan back to their home base. Then, you should be able to wipe out the entire cell at once, and give the others reason to think twice before trying something like this."
// AcceptString :
"P2800846747" "Avoid the trap and take out the Malta operative cell that set it."
// SendOffString :
"P3553484267" "The Malta grew tired of waiting for you already. Your surveillance has revealed the location of the cell's headquarters."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P369740210" "Take down the Malta cell!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2146524636" "You still have a Malta cell to take down, it's time to follow them back to their headquarters and take them down."
// TaskTitle :
"P4027250279" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Blatantly Fake Malta Plans</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P324319832" "From the sound of the grumbling ahead, the Malta are none too pleased you escaped their grasp. Now the hunters become the hunted."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P707549317" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Blatantly Fake Malta Plans</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You took out an entire Malta cell, but risked the life of an innocent hostage in the process.  Someone has to make difficult choices that others are too weak or unwilling to make."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P4194068618" "<shout>Why didn't the hero show?"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1860050195" "<shout>Or maybe they were smart!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3156584478" "<shout>Maybe they didn't even find the files."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2513775894" "<shout>I misjudged our opponent, but we'll try again."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P756961801" "<shout>Clever {Hero.gender=Male boy|girl}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P2067324442" "So you thought you'd ambush us, eh?"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2156970977" "You'll find we're not so easily stopped."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3151074346" "We have ample forces here to keep you occupied."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3974026856" "Don't think we're through yet!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P3150254658" "Yes? I did misjudge you..."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P3832733923" "That's one way to take care of a hero."

