// Clue - ZielenskiClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3738027718" "Save Pello"
// DetailString :
"P41004747" "Officer Zielinski is known for being incredibly rash and reckless, but he usually gets the job done.  That is after his partner pulls his behind out of the fire.  This time they're both in a jam and he's requested your help."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - PelloClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P19613438" "Save Zielinski"
// DetailString :
"P1564534294" "You saved Officer Pello.  She practically demanded that you save her hotheaded clumsy partner Officer Zielinski.  It seems that they thought they would get all the glory by handling this situation by themselves, but this was obviously a job for a hero."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1924398268" "Nemesis has had to abandon bases before. He loves to leave behind an explosive surprise for the heroes or cops who find the base. His trap means you won't have a chance to go after the decoding equipment.<br><br>If you hurry, you can reach the base before they've finished evacuating and defuse the bombs that have been left behind. If you don't, you'd be putting PPD lives needlessly at risk."
// AcceptString :
"P2638783835" "Protect the PPD by defusing the booby traps in the compromised Nemesis base."
// SendOffString :
"P2077464890" "It won't take them long to finish rigging the base."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1495769104" "Defuse the Nemesis Booby Trap!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P151148728" "A PPD are in danger of falling into a Nemesis trap, you need to disarm those bombs."
// TaskTitle :
"P2322294796" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Broken Pocket Watch</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P679256027" "There are a handful of Nemesis troops still inside.  It looks like a few officers have already entered the building.  You need to save then and prevent the trap from ensnaring more PPD officers."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P801789551" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Broken Pocket Watch</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You averted disaster by disabling the Nemesis booby trap, but his decoding equipment is nowhere to be found."
// Script Variable PATROLLER1_SEARCHING_DIALOG :
"P1205923068" "<shout>Got to get these bombs spread out for full coverage."
// Script Variable PATROLLER2_SEARCHING_DIALOG :
"P3508950606" "<shout>I'll feel better once we rejoin the others."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2782909318" "Warhulk Overseer"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3046095400" "<shout>Quickly! We don't want to be here when the bombs go off!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1121023760" "<shout>Bah! Too soon!"
// Script Variable BOSS_RUNAWAY_DIALOG :
"P3749706259" "<shout>Sound the retreat!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3429619659" "Don't think you've outsmarted the master."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P164553160" "The sensitive equipment is miles away by now."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P334514630" "After all... I am expendable."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P2956197406" "You shouldn't have come!"

