"P4278912776" "Decoding Thingamabob"
// DetailString :
"P4252367633" "This punched wooden board is apparently essential to decoding Nemesis transmissions. But from the looks of it, you'd say it was the work of a drunk woodpecker."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3535844131" "Nemesis is crafty to a fault. While some of his men take the sensitive equipment from the compromised base, the more expendable half will stay behind to see they aren't followed.<br><br>The PPD should be smart enough to wait until the bombs are defused to proceed, but you can't afford the delay. You'll go immediately to the new rendezvous location and keep the decoding equipment from slipping away."
// AcceptString :
"P675369545" "Go after the Nemesis decoding equipment before it slips away."
// SendOffString :
"P807660912" "The Nemesis forces will be on their guard even while regrouping. Don't drop your guard."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3633772841" "Grab the Nemesis decoder!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P817283710" "You decide to go after the Nemesis decoding equipment.  Doing so will allow you to track down more high ranking Nemesis officers.  You set off to get that equipment."
// TaskTitle :
"P3726306260" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Broken Pocket Watch</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2627275336" "Nemesis probably enjoys sending soldiers who let their base be compromised into the sewers as punishment."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P937511751" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Broken Pocket Watch</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You recovered a vital decoder for Nemesis transmissions, but several PPD were injured by the booby trap he left behind."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2408613742" "<shout>I hate retreating."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2255296381" "<shout>Just be glad we weren't chosen to stay behind."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P4228755415" "<shout>Just great!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1356968216" "<shout>Open fire! We're under attack!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P307291822" "The War Hulk is the largest and most powerful killing machine built by the Prussian Prince of Automatons. It's a veritable walking tank, armed with flamethrowers, storm cannons, and an impressively brutal power claw."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2384200765" "<shout>Yes, master. My part of the decoder is secure"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1080758020" "<shout>How did you follow us?"

