// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Hero_SL8-9_Task_06 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1262254358" "Sister Jocasta has a long and sordid history of performing assassinations and espionage with the Knives of Artemis. Lucky for her you are willing to stomach the distaste of helping such a criminal out of a tight spot.<br><br>But rest assured, you will make sure that she tells the authorities everything she knows about the shadowy mercenary outfit. This all supposes, of course, that you can actually get her out alive."
// AcceptString :
"P3651726631" "Extract Sister Jocasta from the Knives of Artemis in exchange for her information."
// SendOffString :
"P3589637451" "The Knives may already be planning to deal with Jocasta. There's no time to lose."
// ActiveTaskString :
