"P2353127773" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Your Life Story! Wait, What?</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You extracted a Knives of Artemis informant in one piece.  Hopefully she will prove to be a useful ally in taking down the Knives of Artemis."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
