// Script Variable PATROLLER1_SEARCHING_DIALOG :
"P2182786358" "<shout>Quickly! Locate the intruder!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P3700603144" "Sister Jocasta"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_DISPLAYINFO :
"P2184759145" "Sister Jocasta has a rap sheet as long as a football field, but if she's going to turn against the Knives of Artemis it's up to you to see she survives."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2318386666" "<shout>So, Phoebe, you've finally grown the guts to take me on, have you?"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P643858637" "<shout>So you got my message after all, {HeroName}."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3810862455" "<shout>Traitors don't deserve the mercy of a clean death."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2114962489" "Sister Phoebe"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1638820534" "<shout>You've gotten on my nerves for the last time, Jocasta.<em>Your power play has failed, and you're all alone now."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P344647723" "<shout>Couldn't fight your battles for yourself, eh Jocasta?"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3833406889" "You're helping a vicious woman, {HeroName}."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1474981231" "Jocasta picked a tough one to back her, that's for sure."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P3399217147" "Don't turn your back on her..."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P2031100037" "You're next, Jocasta!"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P321045164" "Excellent.<em>Let's book it out of here."
