// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL8-9_Task_06 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P4248939507" "Sister Jocasta is a notorious assassin who's been involved in the internal power struggles of the Knives of Artemis for quite some time, squabbles you don't want any part in. If she wants your help, it's only to exploit it somehow. Her crimes cannot, and should not be forgotten.<br><br>Her message to you is enough evidence to convince the Knives that she's become too much of a liability to keep around any more. Roughing Sister Jocasta up will let others know you're not interested in being fooled by a villain. Leaving her message behind for the Knives to find means they'll take care of her themselves."
// AcceptString :
"P1968898368" "Force Sister Jocasta to pay for her crimes by exposing her as a traitor."
// SendOffString :
"P516985285" "The Knives won't allow you to just walk in there. Be ready."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3737085223" "Deal with Sister Jocasta!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1830324995" "You've decided the best way to deal with Sister Jocasta is to reveal her as a traitor to her own people and let them deal with her."
// TaskTitle :
"P1551689259" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Your Life Story! Wait, What?</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1886815506" "This is where Sister Jocasta said she'd be. Looks like the Knives followed her."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P4073651251" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Your Life Story! Wait, What?</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You've taken care of a dangerous mercenary assassin, but through decidedly extra-legal methods."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P482008459" "<shout>Why does Sister Phoebe suspect Jocasta of treason?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3169559145" "<shout>I'm sure she has good reason."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P4099716322" "<shout>A hero's good enough reason for me!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P1798287677" "Sister Jocasta is a cold-blooded assassin who has tried to advance her status in the Knives of Artemis for years. Her machinations are about to come to an end."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4194119178" "<shout>Where is that blasted hero? Phoebe will be here soon."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2032849850" "<shout>So... I take it you've decided against my generous offer."
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P3549973118" "So be it."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2305348896" "I'll simply find another hero to be my patsy."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1346894386" "You're not as slow-witted as I thought."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3973701245" "Have you ever considered a career in assassination?"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P844169567" "Wasn't meant to be..."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P766613380" "Time to write another message."

