// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - ComputerClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2897393343" "Malta Dealings"
// DetailString :
"P997275074" "You search through Freymuth's personal computer to find evidence that he had been working with one of the Malta Directors to bring down some major superpowered threats.  In exchange he's been selling Longbow secrets.  The authorities should know about this."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P4102338876" "Senior Agent Freymuth has a long and decorated history with Longbow. You're sad to see he's been blinded by his anger at the system to resort to acting as judge, jury, and executioner.<br><br>The bulletin states that Freymuth is holed up with a cadre of agents, awaiting the dragnet. Putting a stop to this yourself before things escalate will prevent those loyal to him from having to choose between him and the Corps, and will allow some small measure of healing to begin."
// AcceptString :
"P2457252689" "Take Senior Agent Freymuth into custody on behalf of the Freedom Corps."
// SendOffString :
"P80796704" "Senior Agent Freymuth took justice into his own hands. It's time he answers for that.  You might also be able to discover clues as to what Freymuth has been up to."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2693420580" "Arrest Senior Agent Freymuth!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3018913486" "You decide to bring in Senior Agent Freymuth before someone else with less than honest intentions gets their hands on him."
// TaskTitle :
"P3355780939" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Some Nut on Talk Radio</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1015906528" "You never thought you'd see the day you had to take in one of Longbow's own."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P908913577" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Some Nut on Talk Radio</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You saw to it that the vigilante Longbow Freymuth was taken into custody.  Once again, you prove that no one is above the law and everyone deserves a fair trial.  You also uncovered some damning evidence that proves he has been working with Malta to take down various superpowered targets."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P895532421" "<shout>He was only cleaning up the scum the system refused to deal with."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3359059320" "<shout>Back off or we'll be forced to defend ourselves."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1983177323" "<shout>Agreed. He's being tried in the media."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P499959927" "<shout>We have no beef with you, {HeroName}. Stay out of this."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P320892722" "<shout>I owe Freymuth my life."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2101521057" "<shout>You're after a just man, {HeroName}."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1191801148" "<shout>If he hadn't been there in Nerva, none of us would have gotten out."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1723962960" "<shout>Freymuth is more of a hero than you'll ever be."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P4118807725" "Senior Agent Freymuth"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P1650601224" "Senior Agent Freymuth is a decorated Longbow warden who has resorted to murder in his quest to clean up the streets. He must be brought to justice."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P56818347" "<shout>I'll see that you all get commendations after this blows over.<em>You make me proud."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3794682596" "<shout>No. This is not how it should be."
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P482828339" "I'm not your enemy, {HeroName}. I don't want to fight you."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P485930181" "Can't you see you're playing right into the enemy's hands?"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3559937233" "They want you to take me out, my men and I don't play their games."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P263818138" "The system is broken.<em>You need to realize that."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P4089752570" "I hope you... see the light... Someday."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P3604175536" "Godspeed to the hospital, hero. I hope you aren't injured."

