"P598792862" "Psst! Look, it's {HeroName}. {Hero.gender=Male He|She} got that dirty hero Freymuth off the streets."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL8-9_Task_07 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P454945633" "Senior Agent Freymuth is a highly decorated Longbow warden with a long history of doing what's right, no matter the cost. You're not surprised that the rest of the Freedom Corps and the media is quick to demonize him as a murderer. Those he stands accused of dealing with were all killers themselves, the lowest of the low.<br><br>Right now you might be the only person in the city who understands what Freymuth is going through. And you're certainly the only one who can do anything to help. If Freymuth can elude this dragnet, he'll have an opportunity to clear his name and make his detractors see that he's only doing what's best for the city.<br><br>You may have to bruise a few Longbow in the process but the alternative is to let a good man go to prison."
// AcceptString :
"P3179187217" " Help Senior Agent Freymuth elude the Longbow dragnet."
// SendOffString :
"P2950415779" "Freymuth has been cornered in his own base. The Longbow are closing in."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1643892690" "Assist Senior Agent Freymuth!"
// TaskTitle :
"P1982099270" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Some Nut on Talk Radio</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2423356000" "You wish the Longbow weren't in the way, but they'll recover."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1421114847" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Some Nut on Talk Radio</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You've allowed Senior Agent Freymuth, a vigilante member of Longbow, to escape capture.  The world needs more men like Freymuth.  You don't care what Overdrive says.  Without people like Freymuth and you, who will make the tough choices for the greater good?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P31421380" "<shout>Freymuth is a menace."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P4019716903" "<shout>This is a Freedom Corps matter, {HeroName}."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P996757947" "<shout>I feel really bad about this. I used to go to his poker nights."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2245337847" "<shout>You leave us no choice!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2927753364" "<shout>Has he surrended yet?"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P147239868" "<shout>Get back {HeroName}, or face the consequences!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3240942316" "<shout>If he's anything like I remember him, he doesn't surrender."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3525013625" "<shout>You have no business here!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_DISPLAYINFO :
"P3483664964" "Senior Agent Freymuth is a decorated Longbow warden who has done what's necessary to clean up the streets. He can't be thrown into prison like a common criminal."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1774071724" "<shout>I don't blame you, but I wish you'd reconsider."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3429030804" "<shout>{HeroName}? What are you doing here?"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1840364466" "<shout>You crossed the line, sir."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P244403071" "Senior Agent McElhany"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2075963114" "<shout>I've got to bring you in, Freymuth. I don't have a choice."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1202936579" "<shout>Stand down, {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2676769591" "I can't treat you any differently now."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P115028329" "Don't make me do this! Back off!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2464611830" "Surrender and we'll deal with this sensibly."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P826796673" "Alright... I'll surrender.<em>Get out of here before I get back up."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P3284319447" "Stay down!"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P843637551" "You're beyond words, {HeroName}."
// Script Variable SayOnArrival :
"P3063892675" "I have a few friends in this city still.<em>Keep up the good work out there."
// Script Variable SayOnRecapture :
"P3152545818" "<shout>It's ok. I'm not in the mood for trouble."
// Script Variable SayOnRerescue :
"P3255249951" "You had me going there for a moment."
// Script Variable SayOnStranded :
"P1818110576" "<shout>We've gotten separated! Regroup!"
// Script Variable RescueObjectiveText :
"P4001761784" "Rescue Senior Agent Freymuth"
// Script Variable LeadToObjectiveText :
"P3672763409" "Lead Senior Agent Freymuth out."
// Script Variable WaveShout :
"P558001681" "<shout>Freeze {HeroName}!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - EscortFreymuth 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1900839643" "Overdrive"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2660757443" "I can't let you do this {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2176726062" "What are you thinking?  This man is a murderer."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3004824346" "The right thing to do is to hand Freymuth over so he can stand trial."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P4227076179" "You think you're doing the world a service by letting men like Freymuth go free?"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P4101176950" "Innocent people die when people like you and Freymuth make rash decisions."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P939035282" "...is that what you want?  More... blood on your... hands?"
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P4099841409" "I'm sorry {HeroName}.  I truly am, but you've crossed the line."

