// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Hero_SL8-9_Task_08 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3823364186" "The interactions of all the various groups that make their homes in the caves and lairs beneath the city has always baffled you. But the threat is clear: if the Devouring Earth are allowed to attack the Circle of Thorns through their plan of underground demolition, it could have ripple effects on the surface. The damage could start earthquakes, power outages, maybe even unleash a few demons.<br><br>It'd be better off for everyone involved (unfortunately, also for the Circle) if you put a stop to the plot by cleaning out those tunnels before they are detonated."
// AcceptString :
"P2096011527" "Prevent the Devouring Earth from detonating any underground tunnels."
// SendOffString :
"P493031599" "The Devouring Earth will most likely resort to conventional explosives to finish the job once the tunnel is dug."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2441330364" "Prevent the Underground Detonation!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P956666932" "You can't allow the Devouring Earth and Circle of Thorns's war to cause damage to the surface.  It's time to stop this before it escalates beyond control."
// TaskTitle :
"P2647060245" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>You Can’t Keep Your Balance!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1257721893" "This tunnel wasn't here a few days ago. The Devouring Earth move quickly."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2495354980" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>You Can’t Keep Your Balance!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You prevented the Devouring Earth from destabilizing the city, even protecting a Circle of Thorns base in the process.  However, someone could have easily stole into the Circle's lair and stolen their artifacts.  You hope that the collapse of tunnels buried them under tons of debris."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1068882218" "<shout>No more robes!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1004126778" "<shout>RAAAAAGH!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2178289478" "<shout>No more chants!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2642787918" "<shout>WAAAARG!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2624104614" "The Demolisher"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3598860041" "<shout>Dig!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3082984207" "<shout>RRAAAAAAAGHH!"

