// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL8-9_Task_08 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - CircleArtifact 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2803219176" "Runes of Isteron"
// DetailString :
"P2425359202" "These mystic tokens are ordinarily kept buried deep in the walls of Oranbega. They've only been recently extracted to preserve them from the tunnel's collapse.  The arcane energies that pulse around these artifacts are incredibly unstable and dangerous.  Should these fall into the wrong hands, the results could be catastrophic."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1751628723" "There's no point in sticking your nose into the squabbles of two villain groups. If they destroy each other, great. You realize that you can take advantage of the confusion to gain access to the Circle of Thorns' protected artifacts.<br><br>The Circle is already evacuating the affected section of their lair, and the artifacts in that section are mighty vulnerable. Getting them out of the hands of the Circle would compound the damage done when they lose a section of their ruins to the Devouring Earth. This is a plan you like.<br><br>The tunnels are so far below the surface that the repercussions topside are likely to be minimal at best, and passing up the opportunity to cripple the Circle is hardly worth it."
// AcceptString :
"P3871581184" "Secure the Circle's dangerous artifacts while they evacuate."
// SendOffString :
"P3723373119" "The Circle of Thorns is probably in the midst of a full blown panic right now."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P4267723176" "Capture the Circle Artifacts!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3685999895" "You can't allow those artifacts to fall into someone else's hands.  In the wrong hands they could spell disaster for Paragon City."
// TaskTitle :
"P289972965" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>You Can’t Keep Your Balance!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3569008483" "These sections would normally be overwhelmingly guarded. You've picked a perfect moment to strike."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P673457731" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>You Can’t Keep Your Balance!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You've taken some dangerous artifacts out of the hands of the Circle of Thorns, but allowed the Devouring Earth to demolish some underground tunnels."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3251749436" "<shout>I don't like bringing the Runes into the open like this."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1807742660" "<shout>As if those elementals weren't enough to deal with."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1818274358" "<shout>Would you rather they were lost for all eternity?"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P601413280" "<shout>Protect the Runes!"
// Script Variable PATROLLER1_SEARCHING_DIALOG :
"P3009054504" "<shout>Find that hero before they find the runes!"
// Script Variable PATROLLER2_SEARCHING_DIALOG :
"P2755293282" "<shout>Curse these infernal cave-ins!"

