// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P888136140" "Whatever Crey has taken from Arachnos will be dealt with in due course. What's more important is that Lord Recluse learn you will not stand to see Paragon City violated.<br><br>By moving quickly and brashly, the Arachnos troops are easier to locate than you anticipated. It should be easy enough to confront them before they can do any damage. Stopping them, however, will be a little trickier."
// AcceptString :
"P1310859584" "Halt the Arachnos strike team before it reaches Paragon City."
// SendOffString :
"P3826752506" "The strike team will be expecting a hero, but you can't let that stop you."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P865836285" "Halt the Arachnos team!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1531195662" "Despite the odds, and knowing that you'll likely be attacking a group of Arachnos head on who are expecting you, you decide to halt Arachnos before they reach Paragon City."
// TaskTitle :
"P2909401668" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Shattered Jar of Flesh</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2341300554" "You've managed to get aboard the ship they're using for transport. But they've decided to sacrifice stealth for numbers on this occasion."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1065513073" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Shattered Jar of Flesh</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You kept an Arachnos strike team from causing mayhem within the city."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1231478368" "<shout>Did Tomara tell you what we're after?"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2692013930" "<shout>Here we go! A hero!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P969118909" "<shout>No. And I prefer to keep it that way."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2839104855" "Executioner Gage"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P2419268601" "Only the most trusted Arachnos agents are allowed to lead the Bane Spiders. An agent must be ruthless and efficient to become one of Lord Recluse's personal guardsmen. It is a great honor to be promoted to the position of a Bane Spider Executioner."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2201249426" "<shout>Prepare to make landfall."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P767762340" "<shout>You are not enough to stop this mission."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P561719885" "We expected to go in hot."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2147344310" "I'm not about to turn back now."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P4193988573" "I guess... you were enough."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P312583283" "A little overconfident, weren't we?"

