// Clue Name :
"P2771777198" "Flesh Sample Report"
// DetailString :
"P4171778921" "Crey's report on the flesh sample is inconclusive. They acquired it from an Arachnos defector who claims is it part of a Lord Recluse project, but haven't been able to put all of the information together.<br><br>The report goes on to indicate they have decided to try cloning experiments using the tissue... and that the experiments have gotten loose!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - FleshSamples 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P404545369" "Flesh Samples"
// DetailString :
"P4038612328" "This is the full set of stolen Arachnos flesh samples. Without these Crey should be unable to do any more damage."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P252280798" "That Arachnos strike team won't get very far before it gets stopped. Crey, on the other hand, might be able to bury whatever they've found if pressure isn't put on them immediately.<br><br>You've tracked down the lab from which the flesh sample was stolen, now it's time to head in there and break things until you find out what it means, why Crey is interested, and why Arachnos is trying so hard to stop it."
// AcceptString :
"P280635885" "Recover the stolen Arachnos samples from the Crey lab."
// SendOffString :
"P541531804" "Crey wouldn't make Arachnos angry unless this was an important find. Watch your step in there."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P4151019622" "Recover the Arachnos samples!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2658996583" "You need to get into that Crey lab and recover their flesh samples before they're able to do some serious harm with them."
// TaskTitle :
"P3308467255" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Shattered Jar of Flesh</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

