// DetailString :
"P4183811300" "'Look, I just don't wanna die.  I screwed up, made some bad choices.  I'm willing to pay for my mistakes, just please don't let these crazy people kill me."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - FrancoClue 
