"P2217498508" "I Can't Bear to Look Into Their Eyes?"
// DetailString :
"P507576169" "'Yeah, I messed up bad.  I admit it.  Maybe they'll forgive me.  Maybe they'll hate me.  I don't know if I can live with knowing how I betrayed by own people..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2498611152" "The Whispered Hand is known for their subtlety.  Even in the company of the Carnival of Shadows, these rogue police officers won't see their killers coming before it's too late!  It's up to you to stop the Whispered Hand assassins and rescue the police officers so they can stand trial for their crimes.  However, the Carnies are not likely to appreciate your presence there."
// AcceptString :
"P3716711735" "Stop the Whispered Hand assassins!"
// SendOffString :
"P3424042980" "Those men have broken the trust of those that they serve, and must face justice.  You take note of the location where the Carnies are keeping the police officers and head off. Hopefully you can beat the Whispered Hand assassins there."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3694014871" "Stop the assassinations"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P238028632" "Those police officers don't deserve to die. You should go to where they're holed up and take them in."
// TaskTitle :
"P1657316909" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Out Of The Corner Of Your Eye</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P18252512" "This is where those rogue police officers are holed up.  Sounds like the Carnies have given them a warm welcome."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P736503187" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Out Of The Corner Of Your Eye</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You prevented the Whispered Hand assassins from killing the two rogue police officers.  Even though they were going to be taken into custody by those who were previously their colleagues, they seemed to be happy to leave the company of the Carnies."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P795712318" "So, they just came asking the mistress for help?"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1171933137" "Oh, hello darling.  You weren't invited, but I suppose there's always room for you."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2606181344" "Indeed.  Not sure what they were thinking, but I bet they have some juicy gossip to share with her."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1896337281" "I don't have time for you clowns.  I've got a job to do."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P399373181" "Hey, {HeroName}!  Over here!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P517937105" "Mistress Kira"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2725436178" "Look what the cat dragged in."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2810996230" "My my my!  What a lovely little party we've got here."
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P4250693173" "A thousand thanks, {HeroName}!  If I'm not mistaken, we share a similar goal.  Shall we?"
// Script Variable SayOnRecapture :
"P4041273216" "Oh, crud.  I'll hold them off.  Just save the police officers!"
// Script Variable SayOnRerescue :
"P4274426922" "Let's get going."
// Script Variable SayOnStranded :
"P765896562" "You're too quick for me, {HeroName}.  I don't see where you went."

