// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL8-9_Task_10 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - SilentBlade 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Fighting Text :
"P328270082" "You fight with your mouth?  Why not with your precious 'justice'?"
// Answer Text :
"P3898145311" "Close"
// Page Intro Text :
"P3908470276" "I am ready to accept your 'justice' you wish to deliver.  What is it that you feel you must do?"
// Answer Text :
"P820723992" "I'm putting an end to you once and for all, Silent Blade!"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P2403373697" "Ah, I see. Very well...then I am caught and at your mercy.  Bring down upon my head your most righteous justi--<br><br><color orange>Sounds of commotion come from down the halls.  In the distance you hear your name being called out:</color><br><br><color red>We have you trapped, {HeroName}!  Submit yourself before the might of Arachnos and be judged!</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P458625080" "What manner of trick is this, Silent Blade?"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P2226302570" "It would seem that the predator has become the prey.  As you sought to tree your quarry, so too were you being hounded as well.  There is beauty within that irony."
// Answer Text :
"P1992944635" "I will deal with Arachnos, and then with you."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2289718936" "Those rogue cops are scum and deserve whatever they get.  You're here after the big game: Silent Blade.  You know that if you follow the Whispered Hand assassins long enough, that they'll lead you right to her.  This will be a big win for you, taking down several of the Whispered Hand assassins and their target, Silent Blade, all in one fell swoop.  With Silent Blade forever removed from the face of this world, a powerful lesson will be sent to all those with criminal intent - break the law and it will break YOU!"
// AcceptString :
"P1337473053" "Follow the assassins who are on Silent Blade's trail."
// SendOffString :
"P3531996056" "You follow the Whispered Hand assassin without being noticed and see her enter an old abandoned warehouse in Peregrine Island.  That must be where they believe Silent Blade is."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P877103094" "Capture all the Assassins"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P72334907" "You should follow Silent Blade's trail before it grows cold."
// TaskTitle :
"P4248031097" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Out Of The Corner Of Your Eye</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3288418592" "You're pretty sure this is the place the Whispered Hand assassin went."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2879380128" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Out Of The Corner Of Your Eye</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You were able to stop the Whispering Hand assassins hunting down Silent Blade.  However, the trap you laid for Silent Blade turned out to be a trap laid for you by Arachnos.<br><br>Unfortunately, Silent Blade was able to get away in the aftermath of the battle.  But her parting words were quite true - The justice YOU believe in is the ONLY justice that's important.  And one day, you may be given a chance to prove it to her."
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// - ScriptDef - TimedObjective 
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2693269724" "Leaving the Knives was the best thing I ever did."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1822421714" "Right, now we get to hunt worthy prey like Silent Blade."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3516737923" "I normally don't kill unless I'm paid, but I'll make an exception for you."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2917174520" "Job well done, my friends.  As usual, they didn't see us coming."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P834690849" "Someone followed me here.  Take them down!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - DefeatAssassin1 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P2973380820" "Defeat the Whispered Hand Assassin"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2658200840" "I can hear you panting and heaving as you approach me, whelp.<em t=3>Did you learn nothing from me?"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2746029862" "You are not one of my former novices, {HeroName}.<em t=3>I wonder what drives you to pull the tiger's tail."
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P280724041" "Or are you on a crusade to right all the wrongs in the world?"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2485754590" "Perhaps you still believe in good and evil?<em t=3>Is this what drives you, {HeroName}?<em>There IS no difference, {HeroName}.<em t=3>All that matters is who walks away from the fight.<em t=3>Nothing more."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1705734389" "And perhaps...<em t=3>Perhaps this is where my fight...<em t=3>My fight finally ends..."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P2329560035" "Nooooooooo!"
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P980762035" "Perhaps you did not truly believe in your 'cause'..."
// Script Variable Greeting :
"P2275253406" "Hello there son"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P2166760637" "You have defeated me, {HeroName}. I submit to the justice you intend to mete out."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P2476261432" "Why do you not submit to them, {HeroName}? Do you believe yourself the only one with the right to execute justice?"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P861942576" "I see from your own actions that one does not need to submit to ANYONE'S justice...<em t=3>Just so long as you believe you are in the 'right'?.<em t=3>Thank you for the lesson.  Goodbye, {HeroName}."

