// Clue Name :
"P3745438506" "Ravenstorm's Hesitance"
// DetailString :
"P1517894666" "This hero of Paragon City has had a dark past, but has managed to redeem himself in the eyes of the people.  However, he still has a hard time working with unfamiliar heroes, but he knows there's too much at stake to care about that now."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - HeroClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3415781178" "Hollow Point's Militia"
// DetailString :
"P695717223" "One of the kidnapped heroes gives you the low-down on Hollow Point's militia.  Evidently he has gathered members from like-minded organizations in an effort to overthrow the country's government.  He has a tendency to target patriotic heroes."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3755382483" "You're not sure if Doc Quantum orchestrated this situation or if he just caught wind of it, but none of that matters.  Those heroes need your help - their lives are in danger.  You've heard of Hollow Point's brutality and you're very familiar with the brutality of his ex-Council allies.  Hollow Point plans to make an example out of these patriotic heroes who support this country's government.<br><br>However, you know that saving these patriots will likely mean that Hollow Point will get away."
// AcceptString :
"P2770829194" "Save the subdued heroes."
// SendOffString :
"P3093291306" "You think you've made the right decision.  Hollow Point will answer for his crimes at another time.  You head off to the location given to you by Doc Quantum."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2400383077" "Rescue Subdued Heroes"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1994878532" "There are several heroes who desperately need your help.  They've been unmasked and subdued.  Time is of the essence."
// TaskTitle :
"P48496948" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Doc Quantum's Moral Quandary</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P41586141" "You're here, and the stench is terrible, but that's never stopped you from venturing into the sewers before."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2066898820" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Doc Quantum's Moral Quandary</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You rescued the Paragon City patriotic heroes and were confronted by Doc Quantum himself after rescuing them.  He called you predictable and boring.  You like to think of yourself as consistent."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2699899616" "How much longer until we can kill these jerks?"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P246644835" "A hero!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3729632128" "<t=2><t=2>No idea.  I dropped my communicator somewhere in this slime."
// Script Variable PET_NAME :
"P3790904734" "Ravenstorm"
// Script Variable PET_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P215275409" "You're in way over your head here."
// Script Variable PET_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1497031717" "...{HeroName}...I'll accept your help if you'll give it."
// Script Variable SayOnArrival :
"P1351917256" "See ya."
// Script Variable SayOnRecapture :
"P538003493" "Where'd you go?"
// Script Variable SayOnStranded :
"P1164421489" "<shout>Hey! {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable RescueObjectiveText :
"P3079008307" "<color orange>Help Ravenstorm (Optional)</color>"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3581824003" "Militia Leader"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3767347806" "Hah, I think not!  You're outnumbered and outclassed."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2528614381" "Bah!  The numbers appear to be shifitng in your favor."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P2409989984" "Now we fight"
