// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - BlastFurnaceClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3771179101" "Blast Furnace Says..."
// DetailString :
"P4206171844" "Hey {HeroName}, I figured I would find you here.  We both want to stop this jerk before he spread his propaganda over the air waves.  I assume Doc Quantum sent you an 'invite' too?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3839513923" "There was a time when Hollow Point was like you.  He sought to bring justice to the enemies of Paragon City at all costs. He crossed the line, however, and passed over the point of no return.  Hollow Point is currently raiding a local news station; with it, he could spout his hateful anti-government propaganda and draw more people to his militia."
// AcceptString :
"P2961602235" " Stop Hollow Point from raiding the television station."
// SendOffString :
"P296030537" "Scum like Hollow Point have no place in the world, and you'll see to it that he doesn't cause any more problems for this city for awhile.  You head off toward the television station to thwart his little plan.  You don't care what this all means to Doc Quantum, you just feel fortunate to have an opportunity to put this zealot down for the count."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P4020067505" "Defeat Hollow Point"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2184106451" "Hallow Point is raiding a TV station.  This needs to stop!  Now!"
// TaskTitle :
"P1029312811" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Doc Quantum's Moral Quandary</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2328174901" "You can hear orders being barked over the sound of the screams of panicked office workers.  Bingo."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2031606529" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Doc Quantum's Moral Quandary</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You handled Hollow Point and brought him to justice.  He, hopefully, won't be causing any trouble for awhile."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3372897664" "We've gotta round up all these screaming idiots!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P4280884201" "Oh, great...this day just keeps getting better and <i>better</i>!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1232602147" "Round 'em up?  Why not just shoot them?"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P1606485468" "Blast Furnace"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1127308126" "Oh, you're so going down."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2456405627" "Hey hey, {HeroName}!  I thought I might find you here."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P957344940" "Unlikely, you armored cretin."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3266220076" "I see you brought your friends.  No matter. <em t=2> Destroy them all!"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P648457024" "Glad you came along.<em t=2> ...not that I couldn't handle it.  Anyhow, let's stop this Hollow Point jerk by any means necessary!"
// Script Variable SayOnRecapture :
"P2822473491" "I need some help over here."
// Script Variable SayOnRerescue :
"P3930546796" "Let's get back to it."
// Script Variable SayOnStranded :
"P2852116467" "Curse this bulky armor, I can't keep up!"

