"P1864723746" "Oh crud.  A hand please?"
// Script Variable SayOnRerescue :
"P87170157" "I knew you'd be back.<em t=2> Couldn't get enough of me, could you?"
// Script Variable SayOnStranded :
"P1220197438" "Whew!<em t=2> You're too quick for me, {HeroName}.  Wait up!"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_NAME :
"P2105246848" "Colonel"
