"P35901438" "I swear I ran into this guy yesterday who looked <i>just</i> like me.  When I confronted them, they just ran off making crazy robot sounds.  This city gets weirder and weirder by the day."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL8-9_Task_12 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - CrateClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3545616320" "Destroyed Hero Automaton Parts"
// DetailString :
"P4250947580" "You destroy this crate full of enough automaton parts to build half a dozen of Paragon City's most well known heroes!  Nemesis could have bred suspicion between the heroes of the city with these automatons."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - PresidentClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1149915474" "A Familiar Face"
// DetailString :
"P1161903238" "After destroying the crate, a head of an automaton with a familiar face rolls to your feet.  The robotic head of the President of the United States of America stares at you blankly.  Just how far up does this scheme go?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - AutomatonYouClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1680732609" "Crate of Clones"
// DetailString :
"P1541220371" "This entire crate was full of automatons that look exactly like you.  Why Nemesis would need an army of {HeroName} automatons is unclear, but he appeared to have big plans for you."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P364581633" "People like Miss Thystle and Frostfire never really change.  They'll turn over a new leaf for a while, but people always go back to what they know.  If Frostfire wants to redeem himself, let him earn it. <br><br>Somewhere in Peregrine Island there's a warehouse full of Nemesis automatons that need to be destroyed.  If this place is as valuable as Miss Thystle alluded to then you know you're going to be hitting Nemesis right where it hurts."
// AcceptString :
"P92005914" " Stop Nemesis plot by destroying their base."
// SendOffString :
"P1772997295" "Miss Thystle looks on the verge of tears, and for a moment you think she might attack you.  With a mumbled curse she turns around and heads off to where she came from.  Maybe you'll help them after this is all over, if they're still alive.  You head off to the warehouse where all of this is supposedly going down."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P27420910" "Destroy Nemesis Automatons"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P898169076" "You've got a Nemesis Automaton production plant to destroy.  Better head out to take care of that."
// TaskTitle :
"P1165430322" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Miss Thystle's Plea</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P4264286107" "For a moment you think this might be the wrong place. Then you hear the winding and clicking of Jaeger gears."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3342599438" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Miss Thystle's Plea</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>This was a major blow to Nemesis.  You might have even completely stopped his ability to produce automatons in this area.  You know that you did the right thing, despite your actions possibly costing Frostfire his life.  If he dies today, then he'll truly be remembered as a hero. Isn't that what he would have wanted?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P4088023198" "Won't be long now.."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P171463879" "How did you...?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2866240103" "Yeah, another couple hours or so and the heroes of Paragon City won't know who to trust.  The chaos will be epic!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3213509949" "We've been found out!"
