"P969682895" "According to the scraps of text remaining after destroying the altar, it looks like they were trying to harness the power of an artifact called the Taper of the Frozen Flame to cover Paragon City in several feet of ice!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - PolarShiftClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3206838289" "Polar Shift's Remorse"
// DetailString :
"P2757441729" "After rescuing Polar Shift, she seems remorseful for her actions.  She admits she gets no joy from inflicting harm and misery upon others, but she knows that there is no hope for this world as long as mankind continues down its current path.  Perhaps she can instead show them their errors in a different way."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1876626956" "Polar Shift has wronged many people with her recent actions and has descended into villainy.  However, you know it may not be too late for her to redeem herself.  She views the world as a place that isn't worth saving. Maybe you can change her mind. Doing so will likely throw you directly against Longbow, though."
// AcceptString :
"P3015188137" "Convince Polar Shift to give up the life of villainy."
// SendOffString :
"P2275876466" "Officer Jameson is known as an extremist in his organization who doesn't let things go easily.  By actively hunting down Polar Shift, he is beginning down the very same descent as his prey.  It's time to stop this madness before it escalates beyond a controllable state."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1885217008" "Help Polar Shift"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3544322087" "It might not be too late for Polar Shift.  Maybe you can convince her to change her ways.  Regardless, you should hurry before it's too late."
// TaskTitle :
"P15540890" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Biting Wind</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1868809447" "The arcane reverberations of cast spells echoes through these tunnels."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1749498072" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Biting Wind</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Polar Shift seemed unsure of her decision to destroy Paragon City.  You think you might have gotten through to her.  She admitted she got no joy out of causing harm to others.  Maybe she can make a difference by helping others again."
// Script Variable FIGHTER_ONE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2827190897" "Sweep the area, men!  We need this place clean.  Don't let them finish their ritual!"
// Script Variable FIGHTER_TWO_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2569271231" "Protect the artifact!  Don't let them take the Taper!"
