// IntroString :
"P1559548191" "Once you would have considered Polar Shift an ally, but now she's crossed the line and needs to be put down.  Longbow gives you an opportunity to make this happen."
// AcceptString :
"P4078362416" "Work with Longbow to take down Polar Shift."
// SendOffString :
"P1958564618" "It's time to stop this ritual before it brings a new ice age to Paragon City.  You head off towards the source of the cold, hoping you're not too late.  Today Polar Shift's madness ends."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2344052961" "Stop Polar Shift"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2936333599" "Jameson is in the right.  Polar Shift has crossed that invisible line. She is now the enemy.  That's all there is to it.  You set off to deal with her."
// TaskTitle :
"P701083270" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Biting Wind</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

