"P3589820052" "The sound of chanting and gunfire echoes through the tunnels.  Evidently Longbow is already here."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P386607545" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Biting Wind</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Polar Shift seemed truly regretful for her actions.  After rambling on about how this world will come to an end either by her hand or by some other cause, she burst into tears.  She was taken into Longbow custody and hopefully she won't see the light of day for some time."

