// Task - AM_Hero_SL8-9_Task_14 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - BombClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2843445516" "Overkill"
// DetailString :
"P3971971945" "Blast Furnace must have been really steamed by his encounter with Flambeaux.  These bombs would not only have likely killed her, but they'd do enough damage to the neighboring buildings to bring them down as well."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - MagazineClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2096920911" "Issue of the Paragon Caper"
// DetailString :
"P2254757347" "You've found the reason for Flambeaux's attack.  This office is actually covertly home to the Paragon Caper, a tabloid that focuses mainly on super powered citizens.  This issue has some rather unflattering things to say about Flambeaux.  There's even some choice words for Blast Furnace, calling him a wishy-washy coward for turning his back on the people of Paragon City.  Maybe he's not here for Flambeaux after all."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - BlastFurnaceClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3325759341" "Blast Furnace Spills the Beans"
// DetailString :
"P1093647673" "'Okay.  I'll talk.  I can't stand it, these tabloids think they can publish anything they want!  They think I've turned my back on the people of Paragon!  Can you believe it?  I've done so much for this city, and this is how they repay me?  Malta offered to help me take down Flambeaux, even though that's not what I was after.  I was so desperate to burn this place to the ground I accepted their offer, fully aware of the likelihood that they'd turn on me."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - FlambeauxClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P939905664" "Flambeaux's Reason"
// DetailString :
"P3814405447" "'Idiots!  Why can't they see how great I am?  They called me a turncoat, a villain!  A VILLAIN!  Also, the pictures they took of me were, like, totally awful.  They all deserve to burn."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3236435064" "You're not sure what Flambeaux is doing in that office building, but both she and Blast Furnace are causing significant damage to the building and putting lives in jeopardy.  You've got to get in there and take down Flambeaux and Blast Furnace, as well as get rid of any explosives the vigilante has set up."
// AcceptString :
"P3749728581" "Stop both Flambeaux and Blast Furnace from destroying the office."
// SendOffString :
"P930090758" "What is Blast Furnace thinking?  Does he realize he's going to harm the very people he's sworn to protect by setting up those explosives?  Both Flambeaux and Blast Furnace must face justice for their actions."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3907272927" "Save the Office"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P475905383" "Flambeaux and Blast Furnace causing mayhem in one place?  This can't be good!  You need to get over to that office building and resolve this quickly."
// TaskTitle :
"P3277058740" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Explosion in Peregrine</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1082527633" "Techno music and the sounds of panicked office workers fills the halls of this office, but above the din you can hear the shrill voice of a worked up Flambeaux."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2145947133" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Explosion in Peregrine</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You find out Flambeaux's reason behind attacking the office.  This building is home to a tabloid magazine that frequently attacks heroes and villains of Paragon City for their actions.  Apparently there was an issue recently that called Flambeaux some rather unpleasant things.  The article was accompanied by some really unflattering photos of her.  Apparently this set her off on a rampage."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3040303893" "Man, I dunno about you...but I think this Flambeaux chick is...I dunno...crazy."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P4176840560" "Yeah, maybe.  But, crazy's good sometimes.  More chaos, more mayhem!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2851729965" "Let's get crazy on this fool!"

