"P4033756795" "The Office Worker's Tale"
// DetailString :
"P187018671" "'Thank goodness you showed up.  These Rikti charged in here and started tearing the place apart, literally!  They've blasted a hole into the sewers below, looking for something."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P4072343151" "You can't allow citizens of this city to become endangered while you're on watch.  The lives of several office workers and one of Paragon's own, Stalwart, are in danger.  The cause of this raid must be discovered and eliminated before it's too late."
// AcceptString :
"P4081914817" "Stop the Rikti raid."
// SendOffString :
"P1782606061" "Stalwart's diligence is noble indeed. However, you won't allow him to die while you're on watch.  You head off to the office where the Rikti have launched their raid."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2524829715" "Stop Rikti Raid"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1822013853" "The lives of Stalwart and several officeworkers hang in the balance. You need to get to that office building before it's too late."
// TaskTitle :
"P88252937" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Clever Trap</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1312986669" "The sounds of battle rage on deep within the office.  Stalwart sounds like he is still battling the raiding Rikti."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P4107911645" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Clever Trap</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You saved the office workers, helped out a badly wounded Stalwart and stopped the source of the Rikti raid by destroying the Rikti artifact that lured them here in the first place."
