"P984116410" "Powerful Explosives"
// DetailString :
"P3441190200" "The explosives set up throughout the sewers here are capable of not only collapsing these sewers, but also devastating at least two or three city blocks.  This includes the office building above, where Stalwart is."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2464889768" "Sometimes you have to make tough decisions.  This is one of them.  You've got to go after Shock Treatment so she can't keep causing mayhem.  This whole Rikti Artifact stinks of a distraction or perhaps a trap.  Maybe both.  Either way, today Shock Treatment is going to be brought to justice."
// AcceptString :
"P456425480" "Hunt down Shock Treatment."
// SendOffString :
"P3201236010" "Shock Treatment has got to be stopped before she causes another situation.  You head off to the place where you heard she fled to.  She's likely up to something far more dastardly than just causing Rikti to attack an office building."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2767443673" "Stop Shock Treatment"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1436903716" "Shock Treatment must be brought to justice!  Track her down in the sewers."
// TaskTitle :
"P2876673560" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Clever Trap</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3899731167" "Upon entering, you notice that these sewer tunnels run directly beneath the office building where the Rikti are raiding.  Shock Treatment is up to something."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1573603500" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Clever Trap</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You stopped Shock Treatment's plan to trap heroes in the office building above before blowing the building sky high with powerful explosives planted in the sewer below."

