// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Ajax 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2613930940" "Ajax's Profile"
// DetailString :
"P1577381893" "You found some files in the Longbow base regarding Ajax, the only initial survivor of the Omega Team. After the events on that day, Ajax left the public view. <br><br>When the Omega Team's capsule was opened, Longbow investigated Ajax's whereabouts. They found nothing profound - he has been attempting to drink himself into a stupor all these years, though his invulnerability makes it impossible for him to become truly drunk."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P2618871954" "{HeroName}! What are you doing here?"
// Answer Text :
"P1508620140" "I'm here to warn you about Malta, Commander."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P964610238" "Malta? Wait...is it about the Malta turncoat we have?<br><br>There's no need to be concerned, he's genuine. We've got him in the back right now."
// Answer Text :
"P2072224333" "(Explain the situation to the commander)"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P3144398689" "Malta knows where the base is?! This isn't good...not good at all...<br><br>{HeroName}, we're going to get the agent out of here.<br><br><color orange>A loud explosion can be heard from the far end of the base</color><br><br>Malta! They're here!"
// Answer Text :
"P3889771974" "Get the agent and get out of here now!"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P1370075331" "Right! Good luck, {HeroName}. I won't forget this!<br><br><color orange>The Commander quickly runs off into one of the doors to fetch the Malta agent.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P540051526" "Time to fight some Malta..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3831593450" "Longbow may be good, but there's no way they could possibly hold off against a full assault by Malta agents. Worst of all is that Longbow probably must keep radio silence on this, or else they'll alert even more Malta agents to this man's location! <br><br>If you don't move - and <i>fast</i>, that Longbow base is going to be destroyed by Malta - along with Black Panther 952!"
// AcceptString :
"P536592238" "Save Black Panther 952!"
// SendOffString :
"P237209067" "You make your way to the Longbow base - if you move fast enough, you can get there before Malta does, hopefully in time to prepare the base for the Malta assault!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P470975618" "If Malta gets their hands on Black Panther, it'll mean one less person to help in the fight against their organization."
// TaskTitle :
"P2157785663" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Malta Gunslinger Action Figure</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3126943920" "The Longbow base is quiet - for now. You'd better find the commander of the base and tell him what's going to happen."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P36950696" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Malta Gunslinger Action Figure</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You managed to fend off the large Malta assault squad within the Longbow base, buying the Commander enough time to escape with Black Panther 952. Now Longbow will have plenty to use in the long fight against Malta."

