// Dialog :
"P1702105686" "The Longbow Commander leaves to escape with the Malta agent - you need to cover his exit!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3615838592" "<shout>We've breached the base! Move!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2793766909" "We've found some resistance, alert the rest of the teams! Bring the Sappers!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1288318092" "<shout>Charlie Team has arrived!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P231511120" "<shout>Move move move!"
// Script Variable HERO_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2063575886" "{HeroName}? How did you find out about this? <em t=2>I was lucky to be in this base when they brought in the Malta agent. <em t=2> But if you're here, I get the feeling it means something bad is going to go down.<em t=2>I've got your back, then."
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4027690884" "We've got multiple MHIs! Identified as {HeroName} and Frostfire!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P534975619" "Hit them with everything! EVERYTHING!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1404596410" "Teams are down, I repeat, teams are down!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3033781161" "Blackhawk 5-X is nearly here, put down {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4200772351" "Overwhelm them!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3624247062" "Set them up for Agent Blackhawk!"

