// Objective - Assault 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P3414249290" "Fend off the Malta Assault Team!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3418792950" "Don't let up!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2976712177" "Blackhawk 5-X"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2994205296" "<shout>{HeroName}, you've put up a good fight. But now it's time to put you down!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P3010226177" "Do you think Malta is afraid of you, {HeroName}? Malta fears no one!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2024422882" "We don't take traitors lightly. Especially not ones within our higher ranks."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P277073149" "You helping him will only lead to more destruction! Your kind never considers that!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3406520677" "I won't be beaten here by someone like you!"
