// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Ajax 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1635067524" "Deleted Files"
// DetailString :
"P3113785076" "You searched the Longbow computer for any useful information, only to find that Malta had already cleaned the computer out of all its files by implanting a virus within it. You did find one interesting note though - the virus was made directly by Director 4 of Malta. It might not be much of a clue to the director's identity, but it's a start."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1934586677" "Members of Malta deserve no mercy. They willingly hunt down any super-powered being and destroy them. Just because one of them lost their nerve and now wants to switch sides doesn't mean that everything is just 'fine' now between that agent and everyone else.<br><br>You're also not about to let Malta take that agent back. You're going to bust into that Longbow base and show Black Panther 952 the true meaning of <i>justice</i>."
// AcceptString :
"P2082645424" "Deliver justice to Black Panther 952!"
// SendOffString :
"P1899003241" "You set your mind to the goal - heading into that Longbow base to take down Black Panther 952 - no matter what."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2615230186" "Put down Black Panther 952!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1637353638" "Black Panther 952 won't escape your grasp."
// TaskTitle :
"P3971830496" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Malta Gunslinger Action Figure</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3930705527" "Looks like Malta is already in the base. You'll have to carve a path through them to get to your goal."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1209715899" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Malta Gunslinger Action Figure</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You've taken out Black Panther 952. Longbow won't be able to get any information out of him now, and Malta won't be bothered to use him in his current state. This will show anyone that the path of Malta is one-way - there's no going back once you make that leap."

