"P2165750827" "There Are Others, Too!"
// DetailString :
"P2876317454" "After giving you a large hug in thanks, Miss Francine told you that there were others that were kidnapped by Arachnos - Amanda Vines, the reporter from WPSDR, and some Rikti. <br><br>'You've got to help them! Vines...I think they'll just rough her up, like they usually do. But I heard they're going to <i>feed the Rikti to Arachnoids!</i><br><br>Then when it's all done, they said...oh it's horrible...they're going to unleash Arachnoids into part of the slums in Grandville! You've got to stop them!'"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1553209484" "Arachnos is going to use every trick in the book to keep the people of the Isles oppressed and under their control - to the extent where they'd force people to have more faith in their pawn, Westin Phipps. If the people lose more figures like Amanda Vines from WPSDR, the people who are truly looking out for them, all they'll have left is this puppet of Arachnos.<br><br>You need to make sure the people of the Rogue Isles still have someone they can trust!"
// AcceptString :
"P2839924230" "Save the innocents of the Isles!"
// SendOffString :
"P4269113629" "You'll make use of one of the helicopters in Independence Port to get yourself into the Isles - then it's a matter of following the clues to find out where these people are being kept!"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P498653814" "Save the people of the Isles!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3197171999" "Arachnos won't win this time. Not if you have anything to say about it."
// TaskTitle :
"P1645542175" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>You're a Cruel One, Mr. Phipps</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2804498791" "You've made your way into this warehouse within the heart of Grandville. The people in here don't have long - you need to hurry!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1058893570" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>You're a Cruel One, Mr. Phipps</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You saved everyone in the warehouse from a horrific fate at the hands of Arachnos. The people of the Isles - and also the Rikti Traditionalists - are safer now."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P3089233905" "Miss Francine"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_DISPLAYINFO :
"P481475489" "Miss Francine is a woman who is at the forefront of the battle for the Freakshow - something which the authorities in Arachnos aren't too fond of."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3248179026" "Stop! Leave me alone!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1030481430" "A-a hero?! Thank goodness!"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1955812" "You thought you could run from Arachnos, Francine? You were wrong...now we're going to show you what happens when you defy Arachnos!"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2811303236" "What? The trick with Phipps didn't work? Oh well...kill {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3284354680" "Arachnos Torture Agent"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P600927259" "You had a chance to escape before, Francine. Looks like you should've taken it."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2826794032" "A knight in shining armor now, eh?"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P1397335503" "I can't thank you enough, {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable RescueObjectiveText :
"P2784943813" "people to save!"
// Script Variable RescueObjectiveTextSingular :
"P869394414" "One person remains!"
// Script Variable WaveShout :
"P1936714319" "<shout>Stop {HeroName}!"

