// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P2905786540" "Amanda Vines"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_DISPLAYINFO :
"P1608686051" "Amanda Vines is the famous reporter for WPSDR, known for getting into constant scrapes with Arachnos."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P584939629" "You can't seriously think you're going to get away with this! I'm a reporter, I'm going to tell the world about what happens here!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3136255488" "You're...{HeroName}! <em t=2> Hah! You guys are in BIG trouble now!"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2930593505" "If you care about the safety of your family, Vines, you'll keep your mouth shut and learn your lesson."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3945596334" "What? How did {HeroName} find out about this?!"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P4181755041" "{HeroName}. You. Are. AWESOME! EVERYONE is going to know what happened here today!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - Vines 
