// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P1266383255" "You rescued Amanda Vines!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P588233582" "C'Kelkah"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_DISPLAYINFO :
"P2427073792" "C'Kelkah is a Rikti dimensional travel scientist. She is also one of the leaders of the Rikti Traditionalists."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1704262557" "Confused regarding: Arachnos actions. Peace: Rejected?"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P924706372" "{HeroName}:Savior. Timing: Perfect."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P869948315" "Keep your mouth shut, Rikti. Arachnos has vested interest in keeping this prolonged. Too bad for you, huh?"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2236949828" "Of all the...{HeroName}!"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P396123013" "Myself: Most thankful. Informing: Vanguard."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - Rikti 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P2955080462" "You rescued C'Kelkah!"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3253216958" "<shout>You may have gotten those prisoners, {HeroName}, but I cannot allow you to live."
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P134030168" "Surprised? Don't be. This is a favor I'm doing for Arachnos."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P56879055" "Those people you saved, maybe they help the people of the Isles. Maybe."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P254370436" "But I'm the one who will liberate them. Not any so-called 'heroes'."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3865537089" "If only you would recognize that!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P3261293927" "Until we meet again, {HeroName}...!"

