// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL8-9_Task_17 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P2788941839" "<color orange>Westin Phipps stares down at the ground, putting on his best distressed impression for the cameras. You can feel at least a dozen cameras in this room, all of them catching everything that happens here, broadcasting it back to the people of the Rogue Isles. Westin Phipps looks up, taking notice of you.</color><br><br>{HeroName}! Thank goodness you've arrived! I thought these ruffians in Arachnos would be the end of me! You have to save me, please!"
// Answer Text :
"P2092674651" "I'm not here to save you, Phipps."
// Answer Text :
"P227603023" "(Turn to the cameras to reveal to the world who Phipps really is)"
// Answer Text :
"P646884098" "(Beat the living daylights out of Phipps!)"
// Answer Text :
"P4060782435" "Leave"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P2327961703" "You're not? Then what are you here for, {HeroName}...?<br><br><color orange>Westin Phipps raises his voice, ensuring that he can be heard."
// Answer Text :
"P1787664110" "I'm here deliver vengeance, Phipps, for all the people you've hurt!"
// Page Vengeance Text :
"P2467063469" "Vengenace? For all the people I've hurt? Who have I hurt?!<br><br>I've done nothing but HELP the people of the Isles...and you say you're going to attack me...for what?<br><br>For HELPING people?!"
// Answer Text :
"P1990105365" "I know who you really are Phipps. You can't fool me! (Attack Phipps!)"
// Page Attack Text :
"P651941270" "<color orange>Westin Phipps lets out loud cries of pain, emphasizing each blow you make to anyone watching.</color><br><br>I thought heroes...were meant to help the people...do you not care about the people of the Isles...?!"
// Answer Text :
"P2579559324" "Shut your mouth, Phipps! (Knock out Westin Phipps!)"
// Page KO Text :
"P4274264253" "<color orange>Westin Phipps collapses to the ground, knocked out from your attacks.<br><br>It doesn't seem like anyone in Arachnos is coming to stop you.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P2325205578" "That was for all the people you've hurt, Phipps."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P107781754" "<color orange>You turn to the cameras, explaining to the people the true nature of Westin Phipps - that he is an agent of Arachnos, that he serves to raise the hopes of the people in the Isles, only to <i>crush</i> them, much to his enjoyment. When you finish, you turn to Phipps, who shakes his head sadly.</color><br><br>...I feel pity for you, {HeroName}. That you have fallen for the tricks of Arachnos...who have mercilessly slandered my name...to the point where the people of Paragon believe me to be a <i>villain,</i> of all things!"
// Answer Text :
"P2125063620" "You liar! This is not Arachnos propaganda!"
// Page Liar Text :
"P3414530379" "It's not too late, {HeroName}. You can still free me from the clutches of Arachnos! You can save me from their pain!<br><br> <color orange>Westin Phipps stands up, walking up close to you. He tips his head, covering his face with his hands. He gives you an evil smirk and whispers to you.</color><br><br>You'll never win, {HeroName}. I'll always be a step ahead. And the people of the Isles...will <i>always</i> need me."
// Answer Text :
"P2149243721" "We'll see about that, Phipps. (Attack Westin Phipps!)"
// Page KO2 Text :
"P622063892" "<color orange>You brutally assault Westin Phipps for some time before he slumps to the ground, knocked unconscious.<br><br>It doesn't seem like anyone in Arachnos is coming to stop you.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P169035726" "You'll never win, Phipps. I'll make sure of that."
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P1451479704" "<color orange>You leap at Westin Phipps, beginning a long, brutal beating before he could say a word. You go at it for some time, somewhat surprised that no Arachnos operative tries to stop you. You finally kick Westin Phipps aside a few minutes after he loses consciousness."
// Answer Text :
"P1572259029" "(Kick Phipps again for good measure before leaving)"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P663777428" "Westin Phipps is a man who goes beyond the very term 'evil'. His sick heart knows only pleasure from the suffering of others. You can imagine he might actually be <i>enjoying</i> the beating that Arachnos is giving to him, if only because it will give him opportunities to exploit others.<br><br>You're going to storm into the base where he's being held and give Phipps what he deserves - a beating that will last him a lifetime.<br><br>Even if it's caught on tape for all of the Isles to see...you don't care. Phipps will live knowing that you look over his shoulder, waiting for the chance to beat him to a pulp."
// AcceptString :
"P3208223988" "Beat the snot out of Westin Phipps!"
// SendOffString :
"P793084269" "You snag a ride on board a helicopter and begin your journey to the Rogue Isles. Phipps won't know what hit him."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3534961562" "Beat down Westin Phipps!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2601433722" "Westin Phipps is going to remember this for a very, <i>very</i> long time."
// TaskTitle :
"P1521238881" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>You're a Cruel One, Mr. Phipps</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P436929715" "You've arrived in the base where Phipps is being kept. According to your video feed, the Arachnos lackeys 'torturing' Phipps have given him a moment of respite. Perfect."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1550924678" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>You're a Cruel One, Mr. Phipps</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You return to Paragon, overhearing the uproar in the Isles. The people in the slums see you as a villain, while Phipps has become an even greater savior to them. Not that it matters - you know where the lines are drawn, and get a little satisfaction seeing Westin Phipps on crutches. Let's see how many diabolical plans he can help move forward when he spends most of his time in a bed for the next few weeks."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1058608112" "I don't know how I feel about this with Phipps. It's...I don't know. There's wrong...and then there's WRONG."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2025190542" "Grow a spine. <em t=2> This needs to be done."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P218024478" "{HeroName}...! ...I'm kind of, you know, I'm kind of OK with letting them get to Phipps."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2838759779" "Don't be stupid, put {HeroName} down!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2633190414" "We can't let you get to Phipps, {HeroName}. Even if we WANT to. We can't."
// Script Variable NPC_DIALOG_NAME :
"P1181496310" "Westin Phipps"

