// Objective - Phipps 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P3530505904" "Phipps is thoroughly thrashed!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P3446533265" "Normall Shock Treatment seems all sorts of crazy, but right now she's seething with fury.  It seems taking out Westin Phipps really triggered an emotional response."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2024675249" "Westin!  Noooo!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P787516467" "How could you?  HOW COULD YOU!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P148045682" "Westin!  Say something!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2232831704" "I hate you, {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P672632298" "HATE!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P298802100" "Hate hate HATE HATE!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P3682580124" "Nggh... Westin..."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P3977817815" "Westin!  Darling!  Speak to me!"

