"P2780125523" "You've taken out Shock Treatment."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - TaskSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P1038223914" "Westin Phipps won't be recovering from the beating you gave him anytime soon."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - ReturnSuccess 
