// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P2172594299" "You've destroyed the container of bomb triggers!  Now to find Maelstrom before he realizes you've cornered him in a trap!"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P53737446" "{HeroName}!  I'm over here!  I hope you brought your containers!<em t=3>I'm looking forward to introducing you to my friends!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2358364394" "Well, it looks like you're the only one left with the bomb triggers.<em t=3>By the way, these are my friends...I've been programming them all about you."
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P644065416" "Did you think for a moment I would work with someone the likes of you?<em t=3>You're part of a system that disgusts me, {HeroName}.  People like you need to be exterminated."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2824346883" "Let's cut to chase here.  Hand over your container and we'll end this... Where's your container?"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2228980321" "You son-of-a...YOU DESTROYED THEM?!  THOSE WERE THE ONLY ONES LEFT!!!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P823484591" "You win this battle, {HeroName}.  But the war is only beginning..."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P3014910566" "I can't believe I ever called you 'soldier'"

